Additionally, the paper focuses on generating programs for introductory programming courses, which suggests that it may also belong to the Software Engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. The use of static analysis and program synthesis also suggests that the paper may be relevant to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
